th professional DJ's with our new VR mentor program (beta)\n\nPerform for friends and the world with native live-streaming integrations. We'll help you set up your own VR live-mix show with real-time support. You can even request to play a live set on Tribe XR\u2019s radio show.\n\nJoin our Discord channel and have direct access to the Tribe XR team, mentors and a passionate community of music enthusiasts.\n\nPlease note: This is an early access app and we are adding new features and refinements week by week. We only support Windows 10 at this time.", "short_description": "Hello DJ. Welcome to your VR DJ tool. \n\nTribe XR features a fully functioning pro-style CDJ mix deck. Upload your own music and refine your own unique sound."}]}, "developer_name": "Tribe XR Inc", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.dropbox.com/s/sw8jva5kswf857u/Tribe%20VR%20Privacy%20Policy%2012142017.pdf?dl=0", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.dropbox.com/s/sw8jva5kswf857u/Tribe%20VR%20Privacy%20Policy%2012142017.pdf?dl=0", "publisher_name": "Tribe XR Inc", "support_website_url": "https://discordapp.com/invite/qdhNs2U", "website_url": "https://www.tribexr.com/", "category": "EARLY_ACCESS", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": ["EDUCATIONAL", "MUSIC", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER", "SINGLE_USER", "CO_OP"], "id": "339262744724400"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 26, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "3014142328645998"}, {"status": "PENDING", "id"